Description: OpenClaw personal AI assistant gateway, native on-device.
 Ships a cross-compiled Node.js runtime plus the OpenClaw gateway and runs it as a
 launchd daemon. Configure with `openclaw onboard` over SSH after install.
 ripgrep and fd power file-search agent tools and install automatically via Sileo.
